73097272aebd7fafb672969d90155cb693","tid":1733192,"uid":252356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191118/mobile/bkn-20191118124951249-1118_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191118%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191118124951249-1118_00822_001.html&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2Sukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=8a0d3a61\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191118/mobile/bkn-20191118124951249-1118_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n禁蒙面法覆核案頒判詞　官指施加限制超乎合理所需<br />\n<br />\n政府十月初引用《緊急情況規例條例》（簡稱《緊急法》）訂立俗稱《禁蒙面法》的《禁止蒙面規例》，引起爭議，24名立法會泛民議員及前議員梁國雄提出司法覆核，原訟庭今(18日)頒書面判詞。<br />\n原訟庭裁定，緊急法賦權特首會同行會在任何危害公安的情況下可訂立緊急規例，並不符合《基本法》規定，而禁蒙面法第3(1)(b)(c)(d)條和第5條所施加的限制超乎合理所需。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">法庭在作出上述裁定後並無作任何判令，法官指示案件要作進一步聆訊，讓與訟各方就恰當的濟助與訟費作陳詞。案件安排在本周三(20日)開庭。</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZVs15kA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVs15kA.jpg&h=06061edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n則係如果干犯非法集結，都可以照舊可以用呢條罪入。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"但本身用危害公安做理由既緊急法係違憲<br />\n所以應該成個蒙面法而家都違憲<br />\n除非用立會重新立法<br />\n咁非法集結既蒙面法就應該可以立"},{"pid":"e2303703b9ffdcd78500dfca3bf66dbfcf7b0873","tid":1733192,"uid":45466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbe4b21176ebcb7f8556fef2a828482442920d53","tid":1733192,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d151f85ab22a2ed2ec14459b8a493fa4058ae42","tid":1733192,"uid":45466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d698e73097272aebd7fafb672969d90155cb693","tid":1733192,"uid":252356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/